import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import './Cart.css' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { addToCart, clearCart, decreaseCart, getTotals, removeFromCart } from '../store/CartSlice' import PayButton from '../auth/payButton/PayButton' function Cart() { const navigate = useNavigate() const cart = useSelector((state)=>state.cart) const auth = useSelector((state)=>state.auth) const [open, setOpen] = useState(true) const dispatch = useDispatch() useEffect(()=>{ dispatch(getTotals()) },[cart,dispatch]) const handleRemoveFromCart =(cartItem)=>{ dispatch(removeFromCart(cartItem)) } const handleDecreaseCart = (cartItem)=>{ dispatch(decreaseCart(cartItem)) } const handleIncreaseQuantity = (cartItem)=>{ dispatch(addToCart(cartItem)) } const handleClearCart = ()=>{ dispatch(clearCart()) } return (

סל קניות

{cart.cartItems.length === 0 ? (

Your Cart is currently empty

Start Shopping
) : ( <>

מוצר

מחיר

כמות

סה״כ

{cart.cartItems?.map((cartItem) => (

{cartItem.name}

{/* Add any additional product details here */}
{cartItem.price}
{cartItem.quantity}
{cartItem.totalPrice}
))}
Subtotal: {cart.subtotal}

Shipping, taxes, and discounts calculated at checkout.

)}
) } export default Cart
